Usage: dumpOutVias [-help] [-autogen] [-file <filename>] [-all_via  | -signal  | -all_rule  | -default  | -ndr ]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-all_rule            # dump out vias from all routing rules (bool, optional)
-all_via             # dump out all vias (bool, optional)
-autogen             # dump out auto-gen'ed vias (bool, optional)
-default             # dump out vias of default routing rule (the default)
                     # (bool, optional)
-file <filename>     # output file name (default: 'dump_via.out')
                     # (string, optional)
-ndr                 # dump out vias of nondefault routing rules
                     # (bool, optional)
-signal              # dump out signal vias (bool, optional)